# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file:       cp .env.example .env
# 2. Pick ONE provider below (Groq is easiest and free)
# 3. In your new .env file, replace the lines at the bottom
#    with the values from your chosen provider
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Option 1: Groq  (FREE, no credit card) ──────────────
# Sign up at https://console.groq.com  → API Keys → Create
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=gsk_paste_your_groq_key_here
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.groq.com/openai/v1
# MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ── Option 2: Google AI Studio / Gemini  (FREE, no credit card) ──
# Get key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=paste_your_google_ai_key_here
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/
# MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
# TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ── Option 3: GitHub Models  (FREE with GitHub account) ──
# Generate token at https://github.com/settings/tokens (no special scopes needed)
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=ghp_paste_your_github_token_here
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://models.inference.ai.azure.com
# MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ── Option 4: OpenAI  (paid, needs credit card) ─────────
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-paste_your_openai_key_here
# MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ── Option 5: OpenRouter  (some free models available) ──
# Sign up at https://openrouter.ai  → Keys
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-or-paste_your_key_here
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free
# TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# YOUR SETTINGS  (replace these with your chosen provider's values)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=replace_me
MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
TEMPERATURE=0.2
